{"tid":2303014,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG谷] 90/00後開心行山谷！！！！","createTime":"2020-11-27T14:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T14:21:15.000Z","uid":42217,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d949514fd60a66eaf40acfe49f79985a6e50ac2b","tid":2303014,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"呢家天氣咁舒服，各位巴絲有冇興趣一齊開心行吓山? <br />\n<br />\n行山谷不分男女，互相尊重。新人唔洗怕羞，歡迎自由開團報團。<br />\n<br />\n開心郊遊團、慢腳新手團、攝影打卡團、高手進階團無任歡迎，安全至上，疫情關係，做好防疫，為己為人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣開開心心搵吓朋友仔一齊行山，歡迎填妥google form或留tg id:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeDO2_-465fVz2MOHFnxy8rr7cAc35AlmPJTPw7rHeeo1kw3A/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeDO2_-465fVz2MOHFnxy8rr7cAc35AlmPJTPw7rHeeo1kw3A%2Fviewform&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ChmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=7b5c771b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeDO2_-465fVz2MOHFnxy8rr7cAc35AlmPJTPw7rHeeo1kw3A/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以開開心心一齊行山，體驗香港既另一面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9acd357eaf56c168c81097b4f5c1ea35a5731cd","tid":2303014,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0d9282d9822b1961d7cded53941818a02c92af","tid":2303014,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo